+@ Data load pointers (only load if req & avail):
+@  r4   DL + stride
+@  r10  L
+@  r6   U
+@  r5   UR
+@
+@ Others:
+@  r2   req
+@  r7   req & avail
+@  r3   L + stride
+@  r8   DL + stride * 2
+@  r9   stride * 2
+@  cs   Load U
+@  mi   Load UR
